Install (umbrella SDK):
    pip install "revenium-python-sdk[<provider>]"
    # e.g. pip install "revenium-python-sdk[openai,anthropic]"

Usage:
    from revenium_config import create_usage_metadata
    response = client.chat.completions.create(
        model="gpt-4o-mini",
        messages=[...],
        usage_metadata=create_usage_metadata(...),
    )

Required env vars (loaded automatically by `from dotenv import load_dotenv; load_dotenv()`):
    REVENIUM_METERING_API_KEY=rev_mk_...
    REVENIUM_METERING_BASE_URL=https://api.revenium.ai   (optional, default)
"""

